                  Reprobados
                </p>
              </div>
              <div
                class="text-center p-3 bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-950/20 rounded-lg"
              >
                <p
                  id="acadDesertores"
                  class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400"
                >
